99c1bec3343e89d3","tid":57840,"uid":38684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T18:45:31.000Z","msg":"國境之南<br />\n對於成長既失落描寫得好有味道<br />\n個種毒撚既寂寞，內向，冇人明白<br />\n既感覺好有共鳴<br />\n好似有唔少人屌賴明珠翻譯版差<br />\n<br />\n利申:都係睇賴明珠版，<br />\n努力學習日文睇原版中"},{"pid":"b71e7705c7b426b51bfc77aec7da6d47f94f8c33","tid":57840,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:17:23.000Z","msg":"上年呢個時候左右迷左睇村上，而加睇哂佢d長篇，短篇雜文自傳都睇左幾本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意世界末日與冷酷異境、發條鳥年代記、挪威的森林、人造衛星情人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最唔鍾意就咁啱係樓上提到嘅國境之南太陽之西同1Q84<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477b3784644beb5b0b1be142f25ce4b2b3554d2d","tid":57840,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:29:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔算睇左好多本<br />\n最愛係國境之南呢本<br />\n但老實講村上啲小說睇得多會發現其實有種村上味喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係種筆觸同用字  仲有情節嘅營造<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以話好唔好  但個人覺得睇得多會悶</span><br />\n<br />\n所以幾推薦佢嘅短篇小說同埋散文<br />\n感覺上呢個先係佢嘅領域  好多細緻感情都寫得好好同好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n短篇小說集推薦螢火蟲  <br />\n散文集推薦爵士群像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依句啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係個主題同思想咁多年都冇變過，更甚係裡面嘅象徵都成日重覆，好似井喺挪威的森林、發條鳥年代記、聽風的歌都有出現過；影子喺海邊的卡夫卡同世界末日與冷酷異境都用過；連角色意象羊男都喺尋羊冒險記、舞舞舞（不過呢個係尋羊下集）、圖書館奇譚集出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我又覺得睇得多或睇哂可以更透徹理解某d象徵嘅意義，更可以還原村上建構出黎嘅世界嘅全貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedf21712f5535b526034622bea29edd6991589c","tid":57840,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T22:08:21.000Z","msg":"睇左咁多本 <br />\n<br />\n最深刻係沒有色彩的多崎作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5eee4b2d1e5cc8071214e16876d2791182ad28","tid":57840,"uid":41846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T22:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左咁多本 <br />\n<br />\n最深刻係沒有色彩的多崎作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反而覺得多崎作最悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同沙羅段感情好平 無挪威森林咁深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb56f73f93ca9ec1ae54ef1bc73fa399b9e209bf","tid":57840,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T22:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇左咁多本 <br />\n<br />\n最深刻係沒有色彩的多崎作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反而覺得多崎作最悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同沙羅段感情好平 無挪威森林咁深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反而覺得多崎作最悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同沙羅段感情好平<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淡咁</span></span> 無挪威森林咁深刻"},{"pid":"0bc262a9f2ac1e5c844ac7ab58a1929e310e01e7","tid":57840,"uid":64463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"最正都係世界末日與冷酷異境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01148b0fa37e84b36fcb72dd175f366662f9c6a7","tid":57840,"uid":33534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣想要個好似阿綠既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6581159e380d5aeacaabfb94463d252bd43ddc9","tid":57840,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:41:00.000Z","msg":"淨係睇過<br />\n挪威的森林<br />\n沒有女人的男人們<br />\n1Q84<br />\n<br />\n森林就好睇<br />\n1Q84 1,2幾好 但3麻麻<br />\n沒有女人的男人們都唔錯幾有共嗚"},{"pid":"116d6ddb5334d4643aa4b9aac7760aa423908ab8","tid":57840,"uid":29787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人同我一樣想要個好似阿綠既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n綠子係我女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去小林書店果章好令我嚮往同個咁的女仔有個咁的約會"},{"pid":"9080cb9e5492cfd2ef0982c1a6a362e36a36a8c4","tid":57840,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔覺意見到, 上一上水俾嬌嬌女巴打睇下~ <br />\n<br />\n同意樓上巴打講, 佢d小說睇多左有審美疲勞<br />\n不過對沉迷佢既人黎講, 風格統一係好事黎ge<br />\n<br />\n我自己最鍾意一篇短篇- 神的孩子都在跳舞<br />\n簡直係混然天成... 寫實得黎有少少光怪陸離<br />\n好村上式咁將d苦難艱辛輕輕帶過<br />\n將d善良/人情味放晒出黎閃<br />\n有拍成電影, 想睇搵唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954245b65e4413ed2d5a8c79eeab7eac995e526e","tid":57840,"uid":90248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人同我一樣想要個好似阿綠既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}